New app who dis Long time no update. But the wait is over. Here s the ALL NEW TNT APP! SHINY NEW DESIGN We ve redesigned the whole app from the ground up. Take it for a spin and get a whiff of that new app smell. EXPLORE YOUR FAVORITES A new curated experience means it s now easier than ever to find and dig into your favorite shows and live sports our always fresh collections of your favorite movies! BETTER. AUNT. STABLES The look and feel isn t all that s changed. Under the hood we rebuilt how we stream video on your phone to make it faster and more stable so you can watch all. day. long. STAY TUNED We re just getting started. Keep an eye out for new features and Original content coming soon!

Welcome to the all new TNT app! Video playback is in beautiful HD and more stable than ever. You can now cast to Chromecast and Fire TV Airplay support is on the way . You can even start watching live sports and full episodes before signing in with your TV provider. We ve also added select TBS shows in our new Spotlight section. We hope you enjoy these exciting new features and many more!
